  <official_title>Randomized, Double-blind, Crossover, Placebo-controlled, Adaptive Design Study of Safety, Tolerability, Preliminary Pharmacokinetics, and Pharmacodynamics of Single Ascending Oral Doses of MYK-491 in Patients With Stable Heart Failure</official_title>
