  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this Phase 1 study is to evaluate the safety, tolerability, pharmacokinetics,
      and pharmacodynamics of MYK-491 in patients with DCM and stable heart failure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
